Imports example data set for plotting

Source: R/example_data.R
example_data.Rd

The example data set has the same structure as the banks' data and can be used to explore the plotting possibilities.

example_data

Format

An object of class spec_tbl_df (inherits from tbl_df, tbl, data.frame) with 1170 rows and 8 columns.

Value

A dataframe.
